<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-496] Format of TBF rule name field is not defined</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-496</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre manual should define the format (alphanumeric + &apos;_&apos;)  and length (15 characters) of a TBF rule name field.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is important because there is buffer overflow for the TBF rule name (&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15059&quot; title=&quot;Setting several tbf rules at the same time causes crashes&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15059&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15059&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;): the length is not checked by ptlrpc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
